Sentencas: Exploring advanced cathode materials that have high electrochemical activity and superior thermal compatibility with other components is of great importance for the application of intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical performance of Ca-doped NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the present study, influences of Ca doping on electrochemical and physicochemical properties of NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+delta were studied systematically.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical performance of Ca-doped NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A relatively low thermal expansion coefficient (16.8 x 10(-6) degrees C-1) was obtained for the Ca-doped sample over the temperature range of 25-800 degrees C. Moreover, Ca doping significantly enhanced the electrochemical performance of NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+delta.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical performance of Ca-doped NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The highest densities of power for NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+delta-based single cells at the temperatures of 800 degrees C increased from 1.42 W cm(-2) for x = 0.0 to 1.84 W cm(-2) for x = 0.3.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical performance of Ca-doped NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: This increase in electrochemical performance of NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+delta cathode with Ca doping can be ascribed to enhanced concentrations of oxygen vacancies and higher electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical performance of Ca-doped NdBa1-xCaxCoCuO5+δ as cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells
